[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overtoil</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overtoil
<hw>O`ver*toil"</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To weary excessively; to
exhaust.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Then dozed a while herself, but <qex>overtoiled</qex>⟦br⟧
By that day's grief and travel.</q> <rj><qau>Tennyson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overtone</ent>⟦br⟧
